msg: remoting was failing to call actions taking parameters, due to some confusion on the format of the action identifier and the fact that the JavaIntrospector was wrapping primitive parameters.  Now fixed.  Also changed NakedObjectActionType into a regular enum, simplifying code elsewhere, and made some minor improvements to Identifier
